  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK633">
<l>pirittalum pēṇik koḷalum pirintārp </l>
<l>poruttalum valla tamaiccu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The minister is one who can effect discord (among foes), maintain the good-will of his friends and restore to friendship those who have seceded (from him).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
